```
cryptography>=42.0.0
```

## 4. OAuth redirect URIs to register with each vendor

When registering your app with each vendor, use:
- NGP VAN:      https://your-railway-url.up.railway.app/integrations/callback/ngpvan
- NationBuilder: https://your-railway-url.up.railway.app/integrations/callback/nationbuilder

## 5. Activating an integration

When you get API credentials, update `INTEGRATIONS` dict in app.py:
- Change `"status": "coming_soon"` → `"status": "enabled"`
- Set the env vars above
- The OAuth flow and data mappers are already fully implemented

## 6. Read-only data contract

Imported records are tagged with:
- `source`: provider name (e.g. "ngpvan")
- `source_id`: the record's ID in the source system

These records are NEVER written back to the source. Local edits
(support score, notes, canvass results) are stored only in RouteOps.
